Even though there are some trance-songs in this pack, mostly is happy hardcore or dance. There are many accepted and highly professional djs in the list but the should not be mixed with bad quality, cheesy songs from names you never would have heard from the electronica community. Period.
FYI, people, this is really crappy music in the EDM genre. There is very few good songs, maybe like 5 are good/okay or just tolerable. Majority of it is Eurotrash, as I like to call it.

In fact, I'd go so far as to say that if you really think that these songs are the 'Top 100 Trance and Techno Party Songs of All Time', then you have some terrible taste in music and almost no idea of what Trance should sound like.
